commandotroepen.nl/index.php?l=nl&p=13&year=2001&id=42 |title=Jungle Training Belize&nbsp;- Bezoek BLS |language=Dutch |year=December 2001 |publisher=De Officiele Website van de Commando Stichting (Official Website of the Commando Foundation) |accessdate=2009-10-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.korpscommandotroepen.nl/index.php?l=nl&p=13&year=2004&id=22 |title=Van de Korpscommandant |language=Dutch |year=June 2004 |publisher=De Officiele Website van de Commando Stichting (Official Website of the Commando Foundation) |accessdate=2009-10-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.korpscommandotroepen.nl/index.php?l=nl&p=99 |title=Opleidings en Trainingscompagnie Speciale Operaties (OTCSO) |language=Dutch |publisher=De Officiele Website van de Commando Stichting (Official Website of the Commando Foundation) |accessdate=2009-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dutchdefencepress.com/?p=70 |title=SF Operator Worden is een Speciaal vak Apart |publisher=DDP&nbsp;<U+2014> Dutch Defense Press |date=June 6, 2009 |language=Dutch |accessdate=2009-09-01}}</ref>

